query:
SELECT
                    MIN(l1_batch_number) AS "l1_batch_number?"
                FROM
                    (
                        SELECT
                            MIN(l1_batch_number) AS "l1_batch_number"
                        FROM
                            prover_jobs
                        WHERE
                            status = 'successful'
                            OR aggregation_round < 3
                        GROUP BY
                            l1_batch_number
                        HAVING
                            MAX(aggregation_round) < 3
                    ) AS inn
